<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>26</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Lalpa, Na vangpiekna lul,
 Ka neih u apat kimu;
 Na thu lo chun ka hinnau tawh,
 Ka neih cheng uh bei ina.

[V2]
 Ka hun pak ui, (2)
 Na lungsietna ka muh un. (2)

[V3]
 2. Nangmah lungsietna khut apat,
 Hinna leh sinmawh tincheng;
 Hampa, pakcha-hing tincheng in,
 A muu hi vangpiekna tin.

[V4]
 Pahchakna la, (2)
 Na kawm ah a sa zing ui. (2)

[V5]
 3. Aw ka Lalpau, Bangcheng Siempa,
 Nangmah khutsuok chengcheng hin;
 Lungdawn lungkham a ei Vengpa,
 Pakcha buting ki mahle'ng.

[V6]
 Ei nungsawn ki'n, (2)
 Na deihdan ei sinsak in. (2)

[V7]
 4. Phat leh ni a hung bei zela,
 Khawvel thil hawihhaw a tuoi;
 Ka gitlohnau haw hi Lalpa,
 Na theihna chun a hihgim.

[V8]
 Phat muh ka nuom, (2)
 Na hatna muong zing kawm in. (2)</lyrics>
<title>WORTHY TO PRAISE</title>
</song>